long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Provides helpful url based shortcuts for common destinations. Want to type "c/" in your url box to quickly navigate to your calendar? Now you can!

Included shortcuts:
b/
c/
cl/
cs/
docs/
drive/
m/
moma/
sheets/
slides/
who/

All shortcuts can be overridden with custom destinations from the extension's options page.

Also supports custom shortcuts via the go/ keyword. Type "go/whatever" to create a new go/ shortcut. Type just "go/" to manage your go shortcuts. Shortcuts are synced to your Chrome profile and only visible to you.

Xoogler Shortcuts is open source: https://github.com/gotosleep/Xoogler
